<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/29205825">三国里董卓为什么那么厉害？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="3865215" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">感觉董卓并没有什么功绩，被贬之后再进京却可以废立新帝？</div>


</div>
